    <div class="bio wrapper"><!------BIO --->
                <p>Started in January 2010 with only the desire to play hardcore in an aggressive 
                and raw style and to play as many shows, have as much fun and make as many friends 
                as possible</p>
                <p>Since forming, No Second Chance have gained a reputation for being one 
                of the hardest working and most devoted hardcore bands in Europe. 
                By August 2011, No Second Chance will have played well over 180 shows comprising of 
                4 European Tours, 1 UK Tour, 1 US Tour and countless other weekenders and one off 
                shows in UK/Europe.</p>
                <p>In March 2011, No Second Chance signed a deal with Goodlife 
                Recordings for the release of their debut album, out before summer 2011. 
                We have no booking agents or managers, NSC have earned this reputation off our own 
                backs and through nothing but hard work and the gratefully received support from our 
                friends all around the world. We play shows with friends, to friends and for our friends.</p>
        
                <p>No Second Chance have so far played with the likes of First Blood (US), Lionheart 
                (US), Pay No Respect (UK), My First Failure (Ger), Aborted (B), Rotten Sound (Fin), 
                Agnostic Front (US), Embrace Destruction (ITA), TRC (UK), Lower Than Atlantis (UK), 
                Cold Hard Truth (UK), Prowler (UK), Broken Teeth (UK), Ill Intent (US), Hang The Bastard (UK), 
                Face Your Enemy (ITA), Throats (UK), xEisbergx, (UK/LX) amongst many more.</p>
